{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861702337,"sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","part":{"id":"prt_d799b1c14001hExG4Fq9wbBdVV","messageID":"msg_d799afb8d001q4znA189U5f1WD","sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c975e09b5b6e4a099b0bfb17b74a8544","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: Run a controller that deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when an idle-timeout annotation indicates the sandbox has been inactive beyond a fixed grace period.\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: \n8: ### Requirement: Reconciliation trigger\n9: The system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API version `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, using the manager’s API reader/writer client for get/delete operations.\n10: \n11: #### Scenario: Sandbox watch drives reconcile\n12: - **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` object is created or updated in the cluster\n13: - **WHEN** the manager is running\n14: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object’s namespace and name\n15: \n16: ### Requirement: Idle detection input\n17: The system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the `Sandbox` metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL take no delete action and SHALL return without requeue (unless other logic applies—none in this controller).\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: No annotation means no deletion\n20: - **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` without `last-activity-time`\n21: - **WHEN** reconciliation completes\n22: - **THEN** the sandbox is not deleted and result has zero `RequeueAfter`\n23: \n24: ### Requirement: Idle detection parsing\n25: When the annotation is non-empty, the system SHALL parse it with `time.RFC3339`. On parse error, the system SHALL return `RequeueAfter: 30 seconds` and the parse error.\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: Invalid timestamp requeues\n28: - **GIVEN** annotation value is not RFC3339\n29: - **WHEN** `time.Parse` fails\n30: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: Expiration threshold\n33: The system SHALL define `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`. The system SHALL compute `expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`. When `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`, the system SHALL delete the `Sandbox` resource.\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Idle beyond 15 minutes triggers delete\n36: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to a time more than 15 minutes in the past\n37: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n38: - **THEN** the controller calls delete on the `Sandbox` client object\n39: \n40: #### Scenario: Not yet expired requeues until expiration\n41: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is recent enough that expiration is in the future\n42: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n43: - **THEN** the result is `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)` and no delete occurs\n44: \n45: ### Requirement: Delete idempotency\n46: When delete returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL treat it as success and SHALL return empty result with nil error. Other delete errors SHALL be returned to trigger retry.\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: Already deleted sandbox\n49: - **GIVEN** the API server returns not found on delete\n50: - **WHEN** the reconciler handles the error\n51: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n52: \n53: ### Requirement: Get not found\n54: When get returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL return empty result and nil error.\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: Sandbox removed before reconcile\n57: - **GIVEN** the sandbox no longer exists\n58: - **WHEN** `Get` fails with not found\n59: - **THEN** reconcile returns without error\n60: \n61: ## Requirements (binary / operator)\n62: \n63: ### Requirement: Manager options\n64: The `agentd` binary SHALL construct controller-runtime `Manager` with scheme containing core Kubernetes types and `sandboxv1alpha1` from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`, SHALL disable metrics server (`BindAddress: \"0\"`), and SHALL disable health probe server (`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`).\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Signal-driven shutdown\n67: - **GIVEN** the process runs `mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n68: - **WHEN** SIGTERM/SIGINT is received\n69: - **THEN** the manager stops gracefully per controller-runtime defaults\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup Specification\n\n## Purpose\nRun a controller that deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when an idle-timeout annotation indicates the sandbox has been inactive beyond a fixed grace period.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Reconciliation trigger\nThe system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API version `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, using the manager’s API reader/writer client for get/delete operations.\n\n#### Scenario: Sandbox watch drives reconcile\n- **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` object is created or updated in the cluster\n- **WHEN** the manager is running\n- **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object’s namespace and name\n\n### Requirement: Idle detection input\nThe system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the `Sandbox` metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL take no delete action and SHALL return without requeue (unless other logic applies—none in this controller).\n\n#### Scenario: No annotation means no deletion\n- **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` without `last-activity-time`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md","time":{"start":1775861702311,"end":1775861702335}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861702341,"sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","part":{"id":"prt_d799b19ee001fdepJpyfdocdoD","messageID":"msg_d799afb8d001q4znA189U5f1WD","sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3c8d0dd268af4591aa8cccdee503ea2e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: [To be filled during spec definition]\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: [To be filled during spec definition]\n10: \n11: ## Module\n12: \n13: `pkg/agentd`\n14: \n15: ## Language\n16: \n17: Go 1.24\n18: \n19: ## Size\n20: \n21: S\n22: \n23: ## Scope\n24: \n25: ### In Scope\n26: \n27: [To be filled during spec definition]\n28: \n29: ### Out of Scope\n30: \n31: [To be filled during spec definition]\n32: \n33: ## Impact Analysis\n34: \n35: ### Components Impacted\n36: \n37: [To be filled during spec definition]\n38: \n39: ### Dependencies\n40: \n41: [To be filled during spec definition]\n42: \n43: ### Security Considerations\n44: \n45: [To be filled during spec definition]\n46: \n47: ## Design Decisions\n48: \n49: [To be filled during spec definition]\n50: \n51: ## Alternatives Considered\n52: \n53: [To be filled during spec definition]\n54: \n55: ## Implementation Status\n56: \n57: ### 已完成\n58: \n59: [To be filled during implementation]\n60: \n61: ## Testing Strategy\n62: \n63: ### Unit Tests\n64: \n65: [To be filled during implementation]\n66: \n67: ### Integration Tests\n68: \n69: [To be filled during implementation]\n70: \n71: ## Configuration\n72: \n73: ### 环境变量\n74: \n75: [To be filled during spec definition]\n76: \n77: ## API Specification\n78: \n79: [To be filled during spec definition]\n80: \n81: ## Security Considerations\n82: \n83: [To be filled during spec definition]\n84: \n85: ## Performance Considerations\n86: \n87: [To be filled during spec definition]\n88: \n89: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n90: \n91: [To be filled during spec definition]\n92: \n93: ## References\n94: \n95: [To be filled during spec definition]\n\n(End of file - total 95 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n## Overview\n\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Purpose\n\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Module\n\n`pkg/agentd`\n\n## Language\n\nGo 1.24\n\n## Size\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775861702307,"end":1775861702340}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861702343,"sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","part":{"id":"prt_d799b179f00144VEiI8LIP5QwG","messageID":"msg_d799afb8d001q4znA189U5f1WD","sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-5c5e4a42fc4a4c45a4a1c2cfc504c0f6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 Delta Specification\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: [To be filled during spec definition]\n6: \n7: ## Changes to Existing Specifications\n8: \n9: [To be filled during spec definition]\n10: \n11: ## New Specifications\n12: \n13: [To be filled during spec definition]\n14: \n15: ## Deprecated Specifications\n16: \n17: [To be filled during spec definition]\n18: \n19: ## Migration Notes\n20: \n21: [To be filled during spec definition]\n\n(End of file - total 21 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 Delta Specification\n\n## Overview\n\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Changes to Existing Specifications\n\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## New Specifications\n\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Deprecated Specifications\n\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Migration Notes\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775861702304,"end":1775861702342}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861702347,"sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","part":{"id":"prt_d799b1e86001vip4CSvjO6T3K2","messageID":"msg_d799afb8d001q4znA189U5f1WD","sessionID":"ses_286651b01fferR0rlq8FtKTvRx","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-5881104b94b4432290488a58e0392c7b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 Delta Specification: PicoD JWT 中间件\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 实现 PicoD 模块的 JWT（JSON Web Token）认证中间件，为 AgentCube 平台提供安全的会话认证机制，验证传入请求的 JWT 令牌有效性，确保只有合法的会话才能访问 PicoD 的文件操作和代码执行 API。\n6: \n7: ## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod`\n8: \n9: ## Delta Overview\n10: \n11: 新增 JWT 认证中间件功能，包括 `AuthManager` 用于令牌验证、`AuthMiddleware` Gin 中间件用于请求拦截、以及配套的错误类型和常量定义。系统从环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 加载 RSA 公钥，使用 RS256 算法验证 JWT 令牌，保护 `/api/*` 路由组，公开 `/health` 端点。\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## AuthManager 实现\n16: \n17: ### Requirement: AuthManager 结构体定义\n18: \n19: 系统 SHALL 提供 `AuthManager` 结构体封装认证逻辑，包含 RSA 公钥和读写锁。\n20: \n21: ```go\n22: type AuthManager struct {\n23: \tpublicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n24: \tmutex     sync.RWMutex\n25: }\n26: ```\n27: \n28: ### 场景: 创建 AuthManager 实例结构\n29: \n30: **GIVEN** AuthManager 结构体已定义\n31: **WHEN** 查看结构体字段\n32: **THEN** 包含 publicKey 字段（*rsa.PublicKey 类型）和 mutex 字段（sync.RWMutex 类型）\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ### Requirement: AuthManager 构造函数\n37: \n38: 系统 SHALL 提供 `NewAuthManager` 构造函数，从环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 加载 PEM 格式的 RSA 公钥，解析并验证公钥有效性。\n39: \n40: ```go\n41: func NewAuthManager() (*AuthManager, error)\n42: ```\n43: \n44: ### 场景: 成功创建 AuthManager\n45: \n46: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 已设置为有效的 PEM 格式 RSA 公钥\n47: **WHEN** 调用 `NewAuthManager()`\n48: **THEN** 成功解析公钥，返回 *AuthManager 实例，error 为 nil\n49: **AND** publicKey 字段包含有效的 *rsa.PublicKey\n50: \n51: ### 场景: 公钥环境变量未设置\n52: \n53: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 未设置或为空\n54: **WHEN** 调用 `NewAuthManager()`\n55: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n56: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidPublicKey`\n57: **AND** PicoDError.Message 为 \"public key not found\"\n58: **AND** PicoDError.Detail 提示 \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY environment variable is not set\"\n59: \n60: ### 场景: 无效的 PEM 格式\n61: \n62: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 包含无效的 PEM 格式数据\n63: **WHEN** 调用 `NewAuthManager()`\n64: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n65: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidPublicKey`\n66: **AND** PicoDError.Message 为 \"invalid PEM format\"\n67: **AND** PicoDError.Detail 为 \"failed to decode PEM block\"\n68: \n69: ### 场景: 非公钥的 PEM 数据\n70: \n71: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 包含有效的 PEM 格式但不是 RSA 公钥\n72: **WHEN** 调用 `NewAuthManager()`\n73: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n74: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidPublicKey`\n75: **AND** PicoDError.Message 为 \"not an RSA public key\"\n76: \n77: ### 场景: 解析公钥失败\n78: \n79: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 包含格式错误的公钥数据\n80: **WHEN** 调用 `NewAuthManager()`\n81: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n82: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidPublicKey`\n83: **AND** PicoDError.Message 为 \"failed to parse public key\"\n84: **AND** PicoDError.Err 包含底层解析错误\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ### Requirement: 令牌验证方法\n89: \n90: 系统 SHALL 提供 `ValidateToken` 方法，使用 RS256 算法验证 JWT 令牌签名和过期时间，支持 1 分钟时钟偏移容忍。\n91: \n92: ```go\n93: func (am *AuthManager) ValidateToken(tokenString string) (*AuthClaims, error)\n94: ```\n95: \n96: ### 场景: 验证有效的 JWT 令牌\n97: \n98: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n99: **AND** 传入有效的 JWT 令牌字符串\n100: **AND** 令牌使用 RSA 公钥签名\n101: **AND** 令牌未过期\n102: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(tokenString)`\n103: **THEN** 返回 *AuthClaims 实例，error 为 nil\n104: **AND** AuthClaims 包含标准的 jwt.RegisteredClaims\n105: \n106: ### 场景: 验证无效的签名\n107: \n108: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n109: **AND** 传入 JWT 令牌字符串\n110: **AND** 令牌签名不匹配公钥\n111: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(tokenString)`\n112: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n113: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidToken`\n114: \n115: ### 场景: 验证过期的令牌\n116: \n117: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n118: **AND** 传入已过期的 JWT 令牌字符串\n119: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(tokenString)`\n120: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n121: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrTokenExpired`\n122: \n123: ### 场景: 验证格式错误的令牌\n124: \n125: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n126: **AND** 传入格式错误的令牌字符串（非 JWT 格式）\n127: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(tokenString)`\n128: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n129: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidToken`\n130: \n131: ### 场景: 验证空令牌\n132: \n133: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n134: **AND** 传入空字符串\n135: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(\"\")`\n136: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n137: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidToken`\n138: \n139: ### 场景: 验证错误签名算法\n140: \n141: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n142: **AND** 传入使用非 RSA 签名算法（如 HS256）的 JWT 令牌\n143: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(tokenString)`\n144: **THEN** 返回 nil, *PicoDError\n145: **AND** PicoDError.Code 为 `ErrInvalidSignature`\n146: \n147: ### 场景: 时钟偏移容忍\n148: \n149: **GIVEN** AuthManager 已成功初始化\n150: **AND** 传入已轻微过期（< 1 分钟）的 JWT 令牌\n151: **WHEN** 调用 `ValidateToken(tokenString)`\n152: **THEN** 返回 *AuthClaims 实例，error 为 nil\n153: **AND** 使用了 1 分钟的时钟偏移容忍（jwt.WithLeeway(1*time.Minute)）\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ### Requirement: AuthClaims 结构体\n158: \n159: 系统 SHALL 定义 `AuthClaims` 结构体，嵌入标准的 `jwt.RegisteredClaims`。\n160: \n161: ```go\n162: type AuthClaims struct {\n163: \tjwt.RegisteredClaims\n164: }\n165: ```\n166: \n167: ### 场景: AuthClaims 字段验证\n168: \n169: **GIVEN** AuthClaims 结构体已定义\n170: **WHEN** 查看结构体字段\n171: **THEN** 包含 jwt.RegisteredClaims（包含 Issuer、Subject、ExpiresAt、IssuedAt、NotBefore 等标准字段）\n172: \n173: ---\n174: \n175: ## 认证中间件\n176: \n177: ### Requirement: AuthMiddleware 函数\n178: \n179: 系统 SHALL 提供 `AuthMiddleware` Gin 中间件函数，拦截 HTTP 请求，验证 JWT 令牌。\n180: \n181: ```go\n182: func AuthMiddleware(authManager *AuthManager) gin.HandlerFunc\n183: ```\n184: \n185: ### 场景: 中间件函数签名\n186: \n187: **GIVEN** AuthMiddleware 函数已定义\n188: **WHEN** 查看函数签名\n189: **THEN** 接受 *AuthManager 参数\n190: **AND** 返回 gin.HandlerFunc 类型\n191: \n192: ---\n193: \n194: ### Requirement: Authorization 头提取\n195: \n196: 系统 SHALL 从 HTTP 请求头中提取 `Authorization` 头，验证其存在性和格式。\n197: \n198: ### 场景: 缺少 Authorization 头\n199: \n200: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求未包含 `Authorization` 头\n201: **WHEN** 请求通过 AuthMiddleware\n202: **THEN** 中间件中止请求（c.Abort()）\n203: **AND** 返回 401 Unauthorized 状态码\n204: **AND** 响应体包含 JSON: `{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401}`\n205: **AND** 请求不传递给后续处理器\n206: \n207: ### 场景: 无效的 Authorization 头格式\n208: \n209: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含 `Authorization` 头\n210: **AND** 头值不以 \"Bearer \" 前缀开头（例如 \"Basic xxx\" 或 \"Token xxx\"）\n211: **WHEN** 请求通过 AuthMiddleware\n212: **THEN** 中间件中止请求（c.Abort()）\n213: **AND** 返回 401 Unauthorized 状态码\n214: **AND** 响应体包含 JSON: `{\"error\": \"Use Bearer <token> format\", \"code\": 401}`\n215: \n216: ### 场景: 有效的 Authorization 头格式\n217: \n218: **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含 `Authorization` 头\n219: **AND** 头值格式为 \"Bearer <token>\"\n220: **WHEN** 请求通过 AuthMiddleware\n221: **THEN** 提取令牌字符串（去除 \"Bearer \" 前缀）\n222: **AND** 传递给 AuthManager 进行验证\n223: \n224: ---\n225: \n226: ### Requirement: 令牌验证集成\n227: \n228: 系统 SHALL 在中间件中调用 `AuthManager.ValidateToken` 验证令牌，处理验证结果。\n229: \n230: ### 场景: 令牌验证成功\n231: \n232: **GIVEN** Authorization 头包含有效的 Bearer 令牌\n233: **AND** AuthManager.ValidateToken 返回有效的 AuthClaims\n234: **WHEN** 请求通过 AuthMiddleware\n235: **THEN** 将 AuthClaims 存入 Gin 上下文（c.Set(\"claims\", claims)）\n236: **AND** 限制请求体大小为 32MB（http.MaxBytesReader）\n237: **AND** 调用 c.Next() 继续处理请求\n238: \n239: ### 场景: 令牌验证失败\n240: \n241: **GIVEN** Authorization 头包含无效的 Bearer 令牌\n242: **AND** AuthManager.ValidateToken 返回错误\n243: **WHEN** 请求通过 AuthMiddleware\n244: **THEN** 记录警告级别日志（klog.Warningf）\n245: **AND** 中间件中止请求（c.Abort()）\n246: **AND** 返回由 HandleError 生成的错误响应\n247: \n248: ---\n249: \n250: ## 错误类型\n251: \n252: ### Requirement: 认证相关错误常量\n253: \n254: 系统 SHALL 在 `pkg/picod/errors.go` 中定义认证相关的错误代码常量。\n255: \n256: ```go\n257: const (\n258: \tErrMissingAuthHeader = \"MissingAuthHeader\"\n259: \tErrInvalidAuthFormat = \"InvalidAuthFormat\"\n260: \tErrInvalidToken      = \"InvalidToken\"\n261: \tErrInvalidSignature  = \"InvalidSignature\"\n262: \tErrTokenExpired      = \"TokenExpired\"\n263: \tErrInvalidPublicKey  = \"InvalidPublicKey\"\n264: )\n265: ```\n266: \n267: ### 场景: 错误代码定义\n268: \n269: **GIVEN** errors.go 文件存在\n270: **WHEN** 查看认证相关错误代码\n271: **THEN** 定义了 6 个认证相关的错误常量\n272: **AND** 所有常量使用 PascalCase 命名\n273: \n274: ---\n275: \n276: ### Requirement: HTTP 状态码映射\n277: \n278: 系统 SHALL 将认证错误映射到正确的 HTTP 状态码。\n279: \n280: ### 场景: 缺少授权头状态码\n281: \n282: **GIVEN** 错误代码为 `ErrMissingAuthHeader`\n283: **WHEN** 通过 statusCodeMap 查找\n284: **THEN** 映射到 http.StatusUnauthorized (401)\n285: \n286: ### 场景: 无效授权格式状态码\n287: \n288: **GIVEN** 错误代码为 `ErrInvalidAuthFormat`\n289: **WHEN** 通过 statusCodeMap 查找\n290: **THEN** 映射到 http.StatusUnauthorized (401)\n291: \n292: ### 场景: 无效令牌状态码\n293: \n294: **GIVEN** 错误代码为 `ErrInvalidToken`\n295: **WHEN** 通过 statusCodeMap 查找\n296: **THEN** 映射到 http.StatusUnauthorized (401)\n297: \n298: ### 场景: 无效签名状态码\n299: \n300: **GIVEN** 错误代码为 `ErrInvalidSignature`\n301: **WHEN** 通过 statusCodeMap 查找\n302: **THEN** 映射到 http.StatusUnauthorized (401)\n303: \n304: ### 场景: 令牌过期状态码\n305: \n306: **GIVEN** 错误代码为 `ErrTokenExpired`\n307: **WHEN** 通过 statusCodeMap 查找\n308: **THEN** 映射到 http.StatusUnauthorized (401)\n309: \n310: ### 场景: 无效公钥状态码\n311: \n312: **GIVEN** 错误代码为 `ErrInvalidPublicKey`\n313: **WHEN** 通过 statusCodeMap 查找\n314: **THEN** 映射到 http.StatusInternalServerError (500)\n315: \n316: ---\n317: \n318: ## 常量定义\n319: \n320: ### Requirement: 环境变量常量\n321: \n322: 系统 SHALL 在 `pkg/picod/constants.go` 中定义环境变量名称常量。\n323: \n324: ```go\n325: const (\n326: \tPublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"\n327: )\n328: ```\n329: \n330: ### 场景: 公钥环境变量常量\n331: \n332: **GIVEN** constants.go 文件存在\n333: **WHEN** 查看环境变量常量\n334: **THEN** PublicKeyEnvVar 值为 \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"\n335: \n336: ---\n337: \n338: ### Requirement: HTTP 头常量\n339: \n340: 系统 SHALL 定义 HTTP 头名称常量。\n341: \n342: ```go\n343: const (\n344: \tHeaderAuthorization = \"Authorization\"\n345: )\n346: ```\n347: \n348: ### 场景: Authorization 头常量\n349: \n350: **GIVEN** constants.go 文件存在\n351: **WHEN** 查看 HTTP 头常量\n352: **THEN** HeaderAuthorization 值为 \"Authorization\"\n353: \n354: ---\n355: \n356: ### Requirement: 错误消息常量\n357: \n358: 系统 SHALL 定义标准化的错误消息常量。\n359: \n360: ```go\n361: const (\n362: \tErrMsgMissingAuthHeader = \"Missing Authorization header\"\n363: \tErrMsgInvalidAuthFormat = \"Use Bearer <token> format\"\n364: \tErrMsgInvalidToken      = \"Invalid token\"\n365: )\n366: ```\n367: \n368: ### 场景: 错误消息常量定义\n369: \n370: **GIVEN** constants.go 文件存在\n371: **WHEN** 查看错误消息常量\n372: **THEN** ErrMsgMissingAuthHeader 为 \"Missing Authorization header\"\n373: **AND** ErrMsgInvalidAuthFormat 为 \"Use Bearer <token> format\"\n374: **AND** ErrMsgInvalidToken 为 \"Invalid token\"\n375: \n376: ---\n377: \n378: ### Requirement: 请求大小限制常量\n379: \n380: 系统 SHALL 定义最大请求体大小限制常量。\n381: \n382: ```go\n383: const (\n384: \tMaxBodySize = 32 << 20 // 32MB\n385: )\n386: ```\n387: \n388: ### 场景: 最大请求体大小\n389: \n390: **GIVEN** constants.go 文件存在\n391: **WHEN** 查看请求大小常量\n392: **THEN** MaxBodySize 值为 32MB（32 << 20）\n393: \n394: ---\n395: \n396: ## Server 集成\n397: \n398: ### Requirement: Server 结构体扩展\n399: \n400: 系统 SHALL 在 `Server` 结构体中添加 `authManager` 字段。\n401: \n402: ```go\n403: type Server struct {\n404: \tengine           *gin.Engine\n405: \tconfig           Config\n406: \tauthManager      *AuthManager\n407: \t// ... 其他字段\n408: }\n409: ```\n410: \n411: ### 场景: Server 包含 AuthManager\n412: \n413: **GIVEN** Server 结构体已定义\n414: **WHEN** 查看结构体字段\n415: **THEN** 包含 authManager 字段（*AuthManager 类型）\n416: \n417: ---\n418: \n419: ### Requirement: AuthManager 初始化\n420: \n421: 系统 SHALL 在 `NewServer` 构造函数中初始化 `AuthManager`，如果初始化失败则返回错误。\n422: \n423: ### 场景: AuthManager 初始化成功\n424: \n425: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 已设置\n426: **AND** NewAuthManager 成功创建 AuthManager\n427: **WHEN** 调用 `NewServer(config)`\n428: **THEN** AuthManager 被成功初始化\n429: **AND** Server.authManager 字段被设置\n430: **AND** Server 构造成功返回\n431: \n432: ### 场景: AuthManager 初始化失败\n433: \n434: **GIVEN** 环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 未设置或无效\n435: **AND** NewAuthManager 返回错误\n436: **WHEN** 调用 `NewServer(config)`\n437: **THEN** Server 构造失败\n438: **AND** 返回来自 NewAuthManager 的错误\n439: \n440: ---\n441: \n442: ### Requirement: 路由保护\n443: \n444: 系统 SHALL 在 `/api` 路由组应用 `AuthMiddleware`，保护所有业务 API 端点。\n445: \n446: ### 场景: API 路由组受保护\n447: \n448: **GIVEN** Server 已成功初始化\n449: **WHEN** 调用 `registerRoutes()`\n450: **THEN** 创建 `/api` 路由组\n451: **AND** 应用 `AuthMiddleware(s.authManager)` 到该路由组\n452: **AND** 所有 `/api/*` 子路由受中间件保护\n453: \n454: ### 场景: 健康检查端点公开\n455: \n456: **GIVEN** Server 已成功初始化\n457: **WHEN** 调用 `registerRoutes()`\n458: **THEN** `/health` 端点直接注册到 engine\n459: **AND** `/health` 端点不应用 AuthMiddleware\n460: **AND** `/health` 端点可公开访问\n461: \n462: ### 场景: 受保护的路由列表\n463: \n464: **GIVEN** 路由已注册\n465: **WHEN** 查看受保护的路由\n466: **THEN** 以下路由需要认证：\n467:   - `POST /api/execute`\n468:   - `POST /api/files`\n469:   - `GET /api/files`\n470:   - `GET /api/files/*path`\n471: \n472: ---\n473: \n474: ## 错误响应格式\n475: \n476: ### Requirement: 统一的错误响应\n477: \n478: 系统 SHALL 使用统一的 JSON 错误响应格式。\n479: \n480: ```go\n481: type ErrorResponse struct {\n482: \tError  string `json:\"error\"`\n483: \tCode   int    `json:\"code\"`\n484: \tDetail string `json:\"detail,omitempty\"`\n485: }\n486: ```\n487: \n488: ### 场景: 缺少授权头错误响应\n489: \n490: **GIVEN** 请求缺少 Authorization 头\n491: **WHEN** AuthMiddleware 处理请求\n492: **THEN** 返回 JSON 响应：\n493: ```json\n494: {\n495:   \"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\",\n496:   \"code\": 401,\n497:   \"detail\": \"\"\n498: }\n499: ```\n500: \n501: ### 场景: 无效授权格式错误响应\n502: \n503: **GIVEN** Authorization 头格式无效\n504: **WHEN** AuthMiddleware 处理请求\n505: **THEN** 返回 JSON 响应：\n506: ```json\n507: {\n508:   \"error\": \"Use Bearer <token> format\",\n509:   \"code\": 401,\n510:   \"detail\": \"\"\n511: }\n512: ```\n513: \n514: ### 场景: 无效令牌错误响应\n515: \n516: **GIVEN** JWT 令牌验证失败\n517: **WHEN** AuthMiddleware 处理请求\n518: **THEN** 返回 JSON 响应：\n519: ```json\n520: {\n521:   \"error\": \"Invalid token\",\n522:   \"code\": 401,\n523:   \"detail\": \"\"\n524: }\n525: ```\n526: \n527: ---\n528: \n529: ## 日志记录\n530: \n531: ### Requirement: 初始化日志\n532: \n533: 系统 SHALL 在关键初始化步骤记录日志。\n534: \n535: ### 场景: AuthManager 初始化成功日志\n536: \n537: **GIVEN** AuthManager 成功初始化\n538: **WHEN** 初始化完成\n539: **THEN** 记录 INFO 级别日志\n540: **AND** 日志消息为 \"Auth manager initialized successfully\"\n541: \n542: ### 场景: 令牌验证失败日志\n543: \n544: **GIVEN** JWT 令牌验证失败\n545: **WHEN** AuthMiddleware 检测到验证失败\n546: **THEN** 记录 WARNING 级别日志\n547: **AND** 日志消息格式为 \"Token validation failed: %v\"\n548: **AND** 包含错误详情\n549: \n550: ---\n551: \n552: ## 安全考虑\n553: \n554: ### Requirement: 公钥验证\n555: \n556: 系统 SHALL 在启动时严格验证公钥有效性。\n557: \n558: ### 场景: 公钥格式验证\n559: \n560: **GIVEN** 环境变量包含公钥数据\n561: **WHEN** NewAuthManager 执行\n562: **THEN** 验证 PEM 格式解码成功\n563: **AND** 验证公钥类型为 RSA\n564: **AND** 验证 x509 解析成功\n565: \n566: ### 场景: 启动失败策略\n567: \n568: **GIVEN** 公钥验证失败\n569: **WHEN** NewAuthManager 返回错误\n570: **THEN** NewServer 立即失败\n571: **AND** 不启动服务器\n572: \n573: ---\n574: \n575: ### Requirement: 签名算法验证\n576: \n577: 系统 SHALL 拒绝不支持的签名算法。\n578: \n579: ### 场景: 拒绝非 RSA 签名\n580: \n581: **GIVEN** JWT 令牌使用 HS256 签名算法\n582: **WHEN** AuthManager.ValidateToken 验证令牌\n583: **THEN** 检查 token.Method 为 *jwt.SigningMethodRSA 类型\n584: **AND** 如果不是 RSA 算法，返回错误\n585: \n586: ---\n587: \n588: ### Requirement: 请求大小限制\n589: \n590: 系统 SHALL 在认证成功后限制请求体大小。\n591: \n592: ### 场景: 应用请求体大小限制\n593: \n594: **GIVEN** JWT 令牌验证成功\n595: **WHEN** 请求继续处理\n596: **THEN** 使用 http.MaxBytesReader 包装 c.Request.Body\n597: **AND** 限制为 MaxBodySize（32MB）\n598: **AND** 超过限制时返回 413 Payload Too Large\n599: \n600: ---\n601: \n602: ## 并发安全\n603: \n604: ### Requirement: 读取锁保护\n605: \n606: 系统 SHALL 在读取公钥时使用读锁保护并发访问。\n607: \n608: ### 场景: 并发验证令牌\n609: \n610: **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 同时调用 ValidateToken\n611: **WHEN** 读取 publicKey\n612: **THEN** 使用 am.mutex.RLock() 获取读锁\n613: **AND** 验证完成后使用 am.mutex.RUnlock() 释放读锁\n614: **AND** 无竞态条件\n615: \n616: ---\n617: \n618: ## 测试场景\n619: \n620: ### 场景: 单元测试覆盖\n621: \n622: **GIVEN** AuthManager 和 AuthMiddleware 已实现\n623: **WHEN** 编写单元测试\n624: **THEN** 覆盖以下场景：\n625:   - AuthManager 成功初始化\n626:   - AuthManager 初始化失败（公钥未设置）\n627:   - AuthManager 初始化失败（无效 PEM）\n628:   - AuthManager 初始化失败（非 RSA 公钥）\n629:   - 令牌验证成功\n630:   - 令牌验证失败（无效签名）\n631:   - 令牌验证失败（过期）\n632:   - 令牌验证失败（格式错误）\n633:   - 中间件缺少 Authorization 头\n634:   - 中间件无效 Authorization 格式\n635:   - 中间件令牌验证成功\n636:   - 中间件令牌验证失败\n637: \n638: ### 场景: 集成测试覆盖\n639: \n640: **GIVEN** Server 已启动\n641: **WHEN** 执行集成测试\n642: **THEN** 覆盖以下场景：\n643:   - 未认证请求访问 /api/* 返回 401\n644:   - 有效令牌访问 /api/* 返回成功\n645:   - 无效令牌访问 /api/* 返回 401\n646:   - 未认证请求访问 /health 返回成功\n647:   - 公钥未配置时 Server 启动失败\n648: \n649: ---\n650: \n651: ## 依赖项\n652: \n653: ### Requirement: 包导入\n654: \n655: 系统 SHALL 导入以下包：\n656: \n657: ```go\n658: import (\n659: \t\"crypto/rsa\"\n660: \t\"crypto/x509\"\n661: \t\"encoding/pem\"\n662: \t\"os\"\n663: \t\"sync\"\n664: \t\"time\"\n665: \n666: \t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n667: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n668: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n669: )\n670: ```\n671: \n672: ### 场景: 依赖包验证\n673: \n674: **GIVEN** Go 模块已初始化\n675: **WHEN** 查看依赖项\n676: **THEN** 包含 golang-jwt/jwt/v5\n677: **AND** 包含 gin-gonic/gin\n678: **AND** 包含 k8s.io/klog/v2\n679: **AND** 包含标准库 crypto/rsa、crypto/x509、encoding/pem\n680: \n681: ---\n682: \n683: ## 最终验证\n684: \n685: ### 场景: 端到端认证流程\n686: \n687: **GIVEN** Server 已启动并配置有效公钥\n688: **AND** 客户端持有有效的 JWT 令牌\n689: **WHEN** 客户端发送请求到 /api/execute，携带 Authorization: Bearer <token>\n690: **THEN** AuthMiddleware 提取令牌\n691: **AND** AuthManager 验证令牌成功\n692: **AND** 请求传递给处理器\n693: **AND** 返回处理器响应\n694: \n695: ### 场景: 认证失败流程\n696: \n697: **GIVEN** Server 已启动并配置有效公钥\n698: **AND** 客户端持有无效或过期的 JWT 令牌\n699: **WHEN** 客户端发送请求到 /api/execute，携带 Authorization: Bearer <invalid_token>\n700: **THEN** AuthMiddleware 提取令牌\n701: **AND** AuthManager 验证令牌失败\n702: **AND** 中间件中止请求\n703: **AND** 返回 401 Unauthorized 和错误消息\n704: **AND** 记录警告日志\n705: \n706: ### 场景: 健康检查绕过认证\n707: \n708: **GIVEN** Server 已启动并配置有效公钥\n709: **AND** Kubernetes 探针需要检查健康状态\n710: **WHEN** 发送 GET /health 请求，不携带 Authorization 头\n711: **THEN** 请求绕过 AuthMiddleware\n712: **AND** 返回健康状态（200 OK）\n713: \n714: ### 场景: 启动时公钥验证\n715: \n716: **GIVEN** 部署环境未配置 PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\n717: **WHEN** 尝试启动 Server\n718: **THEN** NewServer 返回错误\n719: **AND** 进程退出\n720: **AND** 错误消息指示公钥未配置\n721: \n722: ---\n723: \n724: ## 代码组织\n725: \n726: ### Requirement: 文件结构\n727: \n728: 系统 SHALL 按职责分离认证相关代码。\n729: \n730: ### 场景: 文件组织清晰\n731: \n732: **GIVEN** pkg/picod 目录需要组织认证代码\n733: **WHEN** 查看文件结构\n734: **THEN** 认证相关代码分布在以下文件：\n735:   - `auth.go` - AuthManager 和 AuthClaims\n736:   - `middleware.go` - AuthMiddleware\n737:   - `errors.go` - 错误类型和 HTTP 映射\n738:   - `constants.go` - 环境变量和错误消息常量\n739:   - `server.go` - Server 集成\n740:   - `auth_test.go` - 单元测试\n\n(End of file - total 740 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 Delta Specification: PicoD JWT 中间件\n\n## Purpose\n\n实现 PicoD 模块的 JWT（JSON Web Token）认证中间件，为 AgentCube 平台提供安全的会话认证机制，验证传入请求的 JWT 令牌有效性，确保只有合法的会话才能访问 PicoD 的文件操作和代码执行 API。\n\n## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod`\n\n## Delta Overview\n\n新增 JWT 认证中间件功能，包括 `AuthManager` 用于令牌验证、`AuthMiddleware` Gin 中间件用于请求拦截、以及配套的错误类型和常量定义。系统从环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 加载 RSA 公钥，使用 RS256 算法验证 JWT 令牌，保护 `/api/*` 路由组，公开 `/health` 端点。\n\n---\n\n## AuthManager 实现\n\n### Requirement: AuthManager 结构体定义\n\n系统 SHALL 提供 `AuthManager` 结构体封装认证逻辑，包含 RSA 公钥和读写锁。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775861702314,"end":1775861702344}}}}
